  .grid-container.bg-grd-dark-blue-dark.text-white.medium-mbn5.medium-pb5
    .grid-x.grid-padding-x.align-center.py3.medium-py5.px2.large-px0
      .cell.medium-9.large-7
        :markdown-it(html typographer)
          Our platform provides a proven, established pathway to optimize data migration, storage, structure, security and performance analytics. 
          + Environment and data governance
          + Ethical governance
          + Universal data management & rapid data ingestion
          + End-to-end interactive analytics
          + Self-service data discovery and exploration
          + Context sensitive metadata
        .grid-x.grid-padding-x.small-up-1.medium-up-3
          .cell
            .text-center
              img.mb1.lazyload(data-sizes="auto" data-src="images/icons/icon-data-migrator-white.svg" alt="CHANGE_ME")
              h6 Migrate Data Efficiently
            p Moving to the cloud eliminates the cost associated with legacy systems, freeing both capital and human resources. 

          .cell
            .text-center
              img.mb1.lazyload(data-sizes="auto" data-src="images/icons/icon-data-accuracy-white.svg" alt="CHANGE_ME")
              h6 Improve Data Accuracy and Flexibility
            p Simplify how data is structured and accessed without risking privacy. Implement both proprietary and third-party analytics tools. Eliminate legacy systems and software. 

          .cell
            .text-center
              img.mb1.lazyload(data-sizes="auto" data-src="images/icons/icon-ai-deployment-white.svg" alt="CHANGE_ME")
              h6 Deploy Analytics at Scale
            p Experiment with analytics. Accumulate accurate data sets that can be used to deploy AI. 

  .medium-mbn5.relative.z1
    +callout-panel({
      useVideo: false,
      width: "large-10",
      icon: "images/icons/icon-download-report-blue.svg",
      headline: "The Road To Data Modernization",
      bodyCopy: "A guide to removing barriers on the path to data-driven success",
      buttonText: "DOWNLOAD REPORT",
      link: "https://www.cognizant.com/content/dam/cognizant_foundation/aicom/documents/data-modernization-platform.pdf",
      revealID : null,
      youtubeUrl: "CHANGE_ME"
      })(class="")

  // ======================================================================
  // STAT
  // ======================================================================
  .text-white.text-center.bg-grd-blue-radial.p2.medium-p5.medium-pt8
    .grid-x.grid-margin-x.align-stretch.medium-h100
      .cell
        img.lazyload.mb1(data-sizes="auto" data-src="images/icons/icon-data-platform-white.svg" alt="CHANGE_ME")
        p.font-wide DATA MODERNIZATION PLATFORM
      .cell
        .responsive-embed.stat1
          object.lazyload(data-sizes="auto" data-expand="-100" type="image/svg+xml" data-object="images/stat-data-platform.svg")
      .cell
        h2.mb2 less time
        h5 than platforms built from the ground up
      .cell
