        .grid-x.grid-padding-x.small-up-1.medium-up-3.text-center
          .cell.flex-container(data-aos="fade-left")
            .card.bd0
              .card-section
                img.mb1.lazyload(data-sizes="auto" data-src="images/icons/icon-data-migrator-blue.svg" data-expand="200" alt="CHANGE_ME")
                h6 Enterprise Data Migrator
                p.text-left This pre-built, proven migration engine facilitates modernization of existing data appliances / warehouses / mainframe systems to maximize performance and reduce costs through automated optimization and migration.
              .card-divider
                a.small.button.arrow(href="#") LEARN MORE
          .cell.flex-container(data-aos="fade-up")
            .card.bd0
              .card-section
                img.mb1.lazyload(data-sizes="auto" data-src="images/icons/icon-data-lakes-blue.svg" data-expand="200" alt="CHANGE_ME")
                h6 Enterprise Data Lakes
                p.text-left Provides a seamless orchestration of the various information management and data sciences components coupled with out of the box, industry-grade workbenches required for a data lake build which can elevate it to become a system of intelligence.
              .card-divider
                a.small.button.arrow(href="#") LEARN MORE
          .cell.flex-container(data-aos="fade-right")
            .card.bd0
              .card-section
                img.mb1.lazyload(data-sizes="auto" data-src="images/icons/icon-analytics-blue.svg" data-expand="200" alt="CHANGE_ME")
                h6 Enterprise Analytics
                p.text-left An end-to-end fast data and analytics platform to make sense of the huge volumes of data for accelerating analytics and proliferating business drivers to discover profound insights, make predictions, or generate recommendations.
              .card-divider
                a.small.button.arrow(href="#") LEARN MORE

